location.fullValue: Avon | Residence 39205 Plan, The Overlook at Johnstown Farms

data.description: Welcome to this stunning contemporary home located in The Overlook at Johnstown, offering breathtaking views of the majestic Rocky Mountains. Built just a little over a year ago, this home boasts a modern design with an open floor plan, perfect for today's lifestyle. As you step inside, you're greeted by a bright and airy living space, flooded with natural light from large windows that frame the panoramic views of the Rockies. The spacious living room flows seamlessly into the gourmet kitchen, complete with sleek stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, and a spacious island with seating, making it ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. Adjacent to the kitchen is a dining area with sliding glass doors that open to a deck, providing the perfect spot for enjoying morning coffee or evening sunsets against the backdrop of the mountains. The main level also features a luxurious master suite retreat, complete with a spa-like en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms and another full bathroom offer plenty of space for family or guests. Downstairs, the unfinished walkout basement presents an opportunity to customize and expand the living space to suit your needs, whether it be a home theater, gym, or additional bedrooms. All of this plus the added bonus of solar to help offset the cost of utilities. Conveniently located in the heart of Johnstown, this home offers easy access to downtown amenities, including shops, restaurants, and parks. With quick access to I-25, commuting to nearby cities such as Fort Collins or Denver is a breeze. Whether you're relaxing on the deck, taking in the mountain views, or exploring all that Johnstown has to offer, this home provides the perfect combination of modern luxury, convenience, and natural beauty. Welcome home to The Overlook at Johnstown.
